'''宾得 K-x''' 是一台12.4[[百万像素|百万像素]]的[[数码单镜反光相机|数码单镜反光相机]]，在2009年9月16日发布<ref>{{cite press release | url = http://www.pentax.jp/english/news/2009/200918.html | publisher = Pentax imaging | date = 2009-09-16 | title = PENTAX K-x: A High-Performance Entry-Class Digital SLR Camera, Packaging Movie Recording, High-Speed Continuous Shooting and User-Friendly Operation in Compact, Lightweight Body | access-date = 2010-08-17 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20110104162017/http://www.pentax.jp/english/news/2009/200918.html | archive-date = 2011-01-04 | dead-url = yes }}</ref>。

K-x被认为是入门级的单反[[宾得_K-m|宾得 K-m]]的继承与升级。它比其他宾得的数码单镜头反光相机更加轻量化，包括 K-m 在内，并且与[[宾得_K200D|K200D]]，[[宾得_K20D|K20D]]和[[宾得_K-7|K-7]]相比较，去除了[[防水|防水]]功能，并且附带更加轻量化的DA-L系列套头。它也拥有很多高端机型K-7所不具备的性能，包括最大达到了12800的[[感光度|ISO]]，并且拥有比其他相机更少的[[噪点|数码杂讯]]，更高的[[快门速度|快门速度]]，达到了1/6000秒，已经更加快速的[[连拍|连拍]]，达到了每秒钟4.7张，并可拍摄720p的视频<ref name="dp_pr">{{cite web|url=http://www.dpreview.com/news/0909/09091703pentaxkx.asp|publisher=[[Digital_Photography_Review|Digital Photography Review]]|title=Pentax announces K-x entry level DSLR|date=2009-09-17|accessdate=2009-09-17|archive-date=2011-11-03|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20111103091538/http://www.dpreview.com/news/0909/09091703pentaxkx.asp|dead-url=no}}</ref>。DPReview评价K-x {{cquote|虽然机身外观与K-m一样，却拥有不可思议的多的K-7才拥有的功能。事实上，这款机型的高性能与低价格勾起了人们对于曾经广受欢迎的[[宾得K200D|K200D]]的回忆，这会使得这款机型在中低端领域广受欢迎的<ref name="dp_ho">{{cite web|url=http://www.dpreview.com/news/0909/09091702pentaxKXhandson.asp|title=Pentax K-x brief hands-on|publisher=[[Digital_Photography_Review|Digital Photography Review]]|date=2009-09-17|accessdate=2009-09-17}}</ref>。}}

K-x还提供了一项可选的色彩定制功能使相机有别于传统的黑色单反相机，並提供了更多色彩的選擇<ref name="dp_ho"/>。

[[时代(杂志)|时代]]评选宾得 K-x 为2009年度最佳旅行产品之一。<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.time.com/time/specials/packages/completelist/0,29569,1933520,00.html |title=Time Magazine - |access-date=2010-08-17 |archive-date=2013-03-27 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130327114006/http://www.time.com/time/specials/packages/completelist/0,29569,1933520,00.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>

